headline: Celltrion opens new UK headquarters in Uxbridge, UK
summary: LONDON, June 19, 2025--Celltrion UK has officially opened its new UK headquarters at the Charter Building in Uxbridge, UK, reinforcing the company’s dedication to long-term growth and partnership in the UK market.
